# URL rewrites for the static site.
#
# This file is read by Cloudflare Pages (the live host) and is also understood
# by Netlify, so routing stays identical on either platform. Status 200 is a
# rewrite: the target file is served while the address bar keeps the clean URL.
#
# - "/"      renders the tracker (there is no index.html on purpose)
# - "/today" renders the Today's Games subpage
#
# Dated snapshots are served directly from /snapshots/... and need no rule.

/        /world_cup_tracker.html   200
/today   /today.html              200
